    dc:description "FIGURE 38. A–F, Porrhomma nekolai new species from Chukotka, Christ Bay, Egvekinot Town. A, ♂ carapace, frontal view. B, embolic section. C, epigynum. D–F, vulva, ventral, caudal and dorsal. Scale bars, 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1454812/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

